<section class="block-section reflect">
  <span class="section-tag">Reflect</span>
  <h2>One question before you leave</h2>
  <p class="sub">Three sentences. Three minutes. Use it to plan tomorrow.</p>
  <div class="reflect-input">
    <strong>Prompt — self-assessment vs. success criteria:</strong>
    <br>Rate yourself 1-3 on each success criterion (submitted dossier / rehearsed defense / can articulate strongest objection). Which is your weakest right now? What will you do before tomorrow's defense to strengthen it?
    <br><br>
    Type your answer in your Reflection Journal, or record a voice memo and drop it in your Drive folder.
  </div>
